[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "卜卜感到忐忑。计划外的这种不确定性非但没能给她带来兴奋和冲动，反而让她感到窒息和惶恐。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她害怕失败。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但刚刚那会儿，实在是按捺不住心头的躁郁。猫汐尔就可以做到和陶沉着高效地沟通，两个人好像你明白我我明白你似的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“我尊重你的决定”，“做你想做的事吧”——陶好像也猜出了猫汐尔在撒谎。不同的是，她们好像真的会占卜一样，知道做出什么选择会得到什么样的结果。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl020_01",
        "zh_CN": "（啊，对……）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "卜卜突然明白自己为什么刚刚那么失态了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "——欲望如此强烈，而自己如此弱小。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl020_02",
        "zh_CN": "（可明明我也……）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "明明自己才是最努力最刻苦的那个。明明大家都很轻松，一点也看不出来那些令人震惊的事迹就是她们完成的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她觉得自己不一样。她只是个外勤人员，因为运气被陶和分析员拔到了这么一个位置。她没有那些天启者身上的可贵品质和傲人天赋。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以她从来没有懈怠过。用上了所有的闲暇时间，只为了有朝一日能证明自己配得上这个位置。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可好像还是失败了。留下playername断后，自己像逃兵一样撤退。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是因为没能完美执行他的命令……吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她感到气馁，又因这种气馁而有一股奔腾的热流涌上了头。因为她突然想起了自己是为了什么才走上这条路的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl020_03",
        "zh_CN": "（——playername。）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "被这股外强中干的气势暂时支撑住了。抬起头——她们已经走到了疗养中心的外围，能看见泰坦还在一波一波从墙壁的缺口走出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "猫汐尔停下了脚步。她猫着腰，摆弄着手上的传感器终端。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl020_04",
        "zh_CN": "你在做什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔莲驱",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl012_01",
        "zh_CN": "计算引导信标的最佳安装位置。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔莲驱",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl012_02",
        "zh_CN": "好了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔莲驱",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl012_03",
        "zh_CN": "你的镜爻可以把我们两个人挡住吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl020_05",
        "zh_CN": "你是说伪装吗？嗯……信标的安装位置在哪里？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "猫汐尔抬起手，传感器终端投射出她们脚下这片区域的3D投影。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所有合适安装引导信标的位置都被标记了出来。无一例外，都处于泰坦群的正中间。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl020_06",
        "zh_CN": "办不到。伪装是通过操纵光线欺骗视觉从而实现的，不是什么隐身魔法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl020_07",
        "zh_CN": "这里的泰坦太多了。镜爻要完全遮蔽住我们的身形，没办法应对这种四面八方的视线。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl020_08",
        "zh_CN": "……等等。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "卜卜忽然抬起头，看向周围的泰坦。泰坦缓慢地向外行进着，并没有注意到不远处的她们。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl020_09",
        "zh_CN": "或许可以！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "镜爻从她身后飞起，在她和猫汐尔的头顶组装完毕。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl020_10",
        "zh_CN": "泰坦很高！只要我们趴得足够低，就能完全遮住……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl020_11",
        "zh_CN": "但没办法像针对一道视线时那么逼真，大概就像披着一层更真一点的伪装。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl020_12",
        "zh_CN": "如果它们不低头，我们又走得慢一点，也许是可以的！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔莲驱",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl012_04",
        "zh_CN": "时间还够，慢慢来吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "像撑着一把伞，两个人半蹲着，走着鸭步，一点一点往泰坦群的中心走去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "卜卜专心操纵着镜爻。很顺利，顺利到她甚至能有心思慌乱一番。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "四周都是泰坦的支撑腿，她也不敢说话。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "卜卜低头去看脸前的镜面。镜爻可以扫描背面的环境，通过镜面进行伪装。也可以把镜面一侧的镜像投射到其他镜爻的镜面上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "只看了一眼，她便觉得浑身的毛都要炸了起来——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl020_13",
        "zh_CN": "猫汐尔……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl020_14",
        "zh_CN": "我们……我们被发现了……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "上百个泰坦同一时间看向了她们。一瞬间，卜卜只觉得头皮发麻。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔莲驱",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl012_05",
        "zh_CN": "跑啊，愣什么！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "背后被猫汐尔猛地推了一把，卜卜立刻反应过来，撤掉了镜爻，跟在猫汐尔身后。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔莲驱",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl012_06",
        "zh_CN": "跟紧我！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "猫汐尔跑在前面，往泰坦站位稀疏的方向突围。可好像有了神志一样——泰坦立刻调整了站位，她们突围方向的防御被收紧了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl020_15",
        "zh_CN": "诶？！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "泰坦们甚至主动放低了身形，防止她们从泰坦的脚下穿过去。它们也并没有急于攻击，而是不断调整着站位，让包围圈更难被突破。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔莲驱",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl012_07",
        "zh_CN": "……有人在控制它们。是苏菲——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "卜卜也想到了这一点。她听见一阵越来越近的哼唱。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "疗养中心围墙的缺口中，苏菲从泰坦的脚下走了出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "砰！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "狙击枪的响声在卜卜的旁边炸开。在看见苏菲的瞬间，猫汐尔已经完成了举枪瞄准射击。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "砰——砰——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "猫汐尔没有停下，狙击枪不断轰鸣着。隔着上百米的距离，第一发子弹击穿了挡在苏菲面前的泰坦的巨手，把它打得粉碎。接下来几枪封死了苏菲所有躲闪的空间。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "还没打空弹匣，猫汐尔却停火了。卜卜已经掏出了双枪，正在掩护猫汐尔的后背。但这些泰坦就像角斗场的观众一样，停在原地，一步也没有逾越。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl020_16",
        "zh_CN": "要冲吗？一起冲进去，和分析员会合！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔莲驱",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl012_08",
        "zh_CN": "等一下。她躲掉了所有子弹……不太对。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "猫汐尔头顶的传感器发出低沉的啸叫声。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔莲驱",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl012_09",
        "zh_CN": "不对。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔莲驱",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl012_10",
        "zh_CN": "她变强了。她的身体参数比上午第一次见面的时候强了不止一点……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔莲驱",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl012_11",
        "zh_CN": "……比我们两个的身体素质还要强。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_girl020_17",
        "zh_CN": "那就打近身！我这两把冲锋枪可不是摆设！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "苏菲无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_sophie_01",
        "zh_CN": "——我不想伤害你们。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "隔着上百米的距离，苏菲的声音却像在耳畔那样低沉。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "苏菲无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep8_sophie_02",
        "zh_CN": "把“丧钟”交给我，我会放你们离开。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
